- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely because the paper discusses using machine learning techniques to generate intention for self-driving cars. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is a possibility because the paper discusses self-driving vehicles. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possibility because the paper discusses using machine learning to teach vehicles to anticipate. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility because the paper discusses predicting the lateral position of vehicles on highways.
